WEBVTT

00:04:29.960 --> 00:04:32.530
Yaani hakuna wakati wa kutosha 
kupata watu sahihi

00:04:32.530 --> 00:04:33.866
kuratibu ugavi,

00:04:33.866 --> 00:04:38.040
na kuunda mtaala mahsusi 
unaowavutia watoto na walimu.

00:04:39.760 --> 00:04:43.736
Lakini vipi kama tungetengeneza 
programu ya kiangazi

00:04:43.760 --> 00:04:47.456
ambayo ingewapa nguvu walimu 
kama makocha wa kufundisha

00:04:47.480 --> 00:04:49.480
kuendeleza waelimishaji watarajiwa?

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:53.456
Vipi kama tungewawezesha 
wasomi wa chuo wa mfano

00:04:53.480 --> 00:04:54.760
kuwa wakufunzi wenza

00:04:55.560 --> 00:04:58.096
kuwasaidia watoto kutambua 
matarajio yao ya chuo?

00:04:58.120 --> 00:05:01.356
Vipi kama tungewawezesha 
watoto wenye ufaulu mkubwa kuwa washauri